#### How to use

Check the [Read Me](https://github.com/nadundesilva/mesh-manager/tree/{{VERSION_TAG}}#how-to-use) for instructions on how to use the Operator.

#### Changelog:

- Features
  - Add support to scale microservice using HPA and kubectl
  - Prevent deletion of mircoservices when there are missing dependants
  - Move defaulting logic to a mutating webhook
- Bug Fixes
  - Fix permission issues in creating sub resources
